Introduction

ONE PACT is a five-member boy group under ARMADA Ent. They debuted on November 30, 2023, with their first mini album Moment.

The meaning of their group name "ONE PACT" is a combination of the words "ONE" (Together) + "PACT" (Impact), which means "To come together to make a big impact".

The name of their fandom, "&HEART" represents the idea of a continuous (&) and inevitable (♡) encounter that defines ONE PACT's existence.
